Ten years ago, An article by Martin Fowler rhetorically asked [Is Design Dead?](http://martinfowler.com/articles/designDead.html) 
While I fully agree with the article's negative answer to the question, I think the question itself stems from the fact that the software development community has not yet reached a consensus on a couple of more fundamental questions:

#### Does Design Exist?


and (assuming it does):

#### What is Design?

